                          CFJ 871

   Statement: On or about 20 April 1996, Morendil committed the Crime of
   Misrepresentation, by posting to the Public Forum a message which e
   did not specifically disclaim as possibly incorrect, but which e knew
   or should reasonably have known to contain falsifications.

