Decision of Justice Chuck: FALSE

I agree with Justice Steve's reasoning, and there is little I could
add.  I would only like to note that a statement made by Morendil
in Exhibit D is misleading:

> I even documented, to the PF, the fact that the Regs had
> been modified (message follows), which any interested Player could
> then have requested under FOIA. ;)

The documentation in the PF followed the deletion of the
temporary Regs, but preceded the addition of the Immaculate
Reg; Morendil implies that the PF announcement was an
announcement of the addition of the Immaculate Reg.

However, this does not affect the Judgement.

